org.forgerock.openam.forgerockrest.utils

Class JsonValueQueryFilterVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.forgerockrest.utils.JsonValueQueryFilterVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.forgerock.util.query.QueryFilterVisitor<Boolean,org.forgerock.json.JsonValue,org.forgerock.json.JsonPointer>

    public class JsonValueQueryFilterVisitor
extends Object
implements org.forgerock.util.query.QueryFilterVisitor<Boolean,org.forgerock.json.JsonValue,org.forgerock.json.JsonPointer>
    A query filter visitor that can be used to test whether a JsonValue matches a given QueryFilter. String operations are compared case-insensitively.
